awards.title: 2 semester Dean List Student
awards.summary: Dean's List distinction for Fall 2021 and Spring 2022. Awarded to students who: (1) earn a semester grade point average of 3.5 or higher based on 12 credits or more taken for a grade, and (2) do not receive grades of W, I, F, or NC for that semester.
